If you are looking for a quick meal and oversized portions, this is not the place for you.  If you are looking for an intimiate setting where you can enjoy quality carefully prepared meals and a friendly neighborhood atmosphere, check out Petit Oven.  The staff is extremely dedicated and offers personalized service seen nowhere else.  Every dish is fresh, wholesome and delicious and the portions are just right, enabling you to enjoy each course.  Dining at Le Petiti Oven is like going to and elegant dinner at a friend's home.  They offer a respite from hurried city life right in the middle of your neighborhood.
